    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/0e0f1ce39ad380290dc4a0430f633a01.avif?t=1771881472\" width=553 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/f41e4ab96f1036a511485d41d18559ec.poster.avif?t=1771881472\" width=1024 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/f41e4ab96f1036a511485d41d18559ec.webm?t=1771881472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/f41e4ab96f1036a511485d41d18559ec.mp4?t=1771881472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our core goal is to bridge the gap from playing Chess, to playing a Wargame and as such, we have created game systems that derive from chess (Grid locked Queen style movements), but incorporate simple mechanics you might find in tabletop Wargames (Like moving your entire army in your turn). In doing this, players who know the basic rules of Chess can jump in and just play without the hassle of a 300 page rulebook.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/2792421cb1a6b104903b688c7180a831.poster.avif?t=1771881472\" width=1024 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/2792421cb1a6b104903b688c7180a831.webm?t=1771881472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/2792421cb1a6b104903b688c7180a831.mp4?t=1771881472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br> <br>So step into the battlefields of <i>Realms at War</i>, a chess-inspired turn-based strategy game where every move can shift the tide of battle. Choose from a wide array of unique fantasy factions, each with unique units, abilities, and playstyles. <br> <br>Whether you face off against cunning players in PvP or test your skills against AI in PvE, no two games are the same. Rogue-like elements add fresh challenges each run, as the equipment and units you bring to the tabletop shape your tactics and outcomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/d95f50bd63c684f475a5bf86c03d25ef.poster.avif?t=1771881472\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/d95f50bd63c684f475a5bf86c03d25ef.webm?t=1771881472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138010/extras/d95f50bd63c684f475a5bf86c03d25ef.mp4?t=1771881472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight across diverse environments, from haunted forests to frozen peaks, where terrain and atmosphere influence your strategy. With countless faction matchups, customizable loadouts, and replay-ability at its core, <i>Realms at War</i> delivers a rich blend of tactical depth and fantasy immersion.</p>",
